[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] 
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Daily Study Plan** — Plan and track daily study tasks across all IELTS skills
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Mistake Notebook** — Record and review mistakes with correction tracking
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Vocabulary Management** — Add, tag, filter, and review words with SM-2 spaced repetition
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] ## Features
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Mock Test Tracker** — Log mock test scores and track band progress over time
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Learning Journey Engine** — Weakness detection, review scheduling, next-best-action recommendations
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Content Library** — Built-in IELTS content with versioned updates
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Progress Analytics** — Charts and stats for study days, hours, skill balance, and band trends
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Skill Tracking** — Log reading, listening, writing, and speaking practice sessions
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Exercise Generator** — AI-powered and rule-based exercise generation
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **AI Tutor Chat** — Messenger-style AI assistant with proactive local messages
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Import/Export** — Full JSON backup and restore with merge/replace modes
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] 
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] ## Tech Stack
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Browser Extension** — Collect vocabulary, sentences, and articles from any webpage
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] 
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Dark Mode** — Light/dark/system theme with design tokens
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] | Layer | Technology |
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **PWA Support** — Install as standalone app, works offline
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] | Framework | React 19 |
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] |-------|-----------|
[2026-07-02T01:13:30.246Z] [INFO] [stderr] | Language | TypeScript 5.8+ (strict mode) |
